  ('medical-tech-moex-01358', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下  列何種細菌接種在特殊培養基Wagatsuma agar上時，通常會出現神奈川現象（Kanagawa phenomenon）？', '["V ibrio parahaemolyticus", "M oraxella catarrhalis", "H aemophilus influenzae", "P seudomonas aeruginosa"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "70ef9911acdf", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cd634ef7f050", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01359', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關腸桿菌科（Enterobacteriaceae）的特性敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["V oges-Proskauer test是針對細菌發酵丙酮酸鹽過程中產生的acetoin做測試", "不  具有cytochrome C oxidase活性，因此不能將tetramethyl-p-phenylenediamine氧化，呈現深藍紫色", "不  具有nitrate reductase，不能將硝酸鹽（nitrate）還原成亞硝酸鹽（nitrite）", "尿  素酶（urease）將urea分解產生氨（ammonia），進而使培養基偏鹼性"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "70ef9911acdf", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cd634ef7f050", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01360', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關霍亂毒素（cholera toxin）的敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["血  清型O1霍亂弧菌（Vibrio cholerae）最常造成流行性霍亂（epidemic cholera），也是唯一會產生霍亂 毒素的血清型", "是  A-B toxin，B次單元蛋白可以與宿主細胞的GM-ganglioside受體結合 1", "抑  制腸細胞（enterocyte）G protein的活化，進而造成cyclic adenosine monophosphate（cAMP）的產量 上升", "可  以促進電解質（electrolytes）由細胞內分泌至腸腔，造成水狀下痢"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "70ef9911acdf", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cd634ef7f050", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
